      .prod-info__content
        p.prod-info__txt 1) The sofa's ergonomic design and plush cushions provide exceptional comfort and support, making it ideal for extended lounging sessions.
        p.prod-info__txt 2) Crafted from premium materials, this sofa combines durability with a luxurious aesthetic, ensuring both style and longevity.
        p.prod-info__txt 3) Its versatile modular configuration allows for easy customization to fit various living spaces, catering to diverse interior design preferences.
        p.prod-info__txt 4) With its contemporary silhouette and timeless appeal, this sofa effortlessly enhances any room's decor, promising sophistication and charm.
        p.prod-info__txt 5) The sofa's innovative reclining mechanism and adjustable headrests offer unparalleled relaxation, perfect for unwinding after a long day.
